Class ADoubleDivergentFractalIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sm.fraxion.fractals.AFractalIterator

        • org.sm.fraxion.fractals.ADoubleDivergentFractalIterator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ManowarFractalIterator, PhoenixFractalIterator

    public abstract class ADoubleDivergentFractalIterator
extends ADivergentFractalIterator
    The ADoubleDivergentFractalIterator class provides a base class for divergent fractal iterators that use z(n) and z(n - 1).

    04/11/2014
